snippet: Reserve Taurean Prince scored 12 of his 15 points in the first half, leading No. 9 Baylor to an 80-50 victory over Savannah State on Friday night....

headline.print_headline: Prince Scores 15, Leads Baylor to Easy Win
headline.main: Prince Scores 15, Leads Baylor to Easy Win

lead_paragraph: Reserve Taurean Prince scored 12 of his 15 points in the first half, leading No. 9 Baylor to an 80-50 victory over Savannah State on Friday night.
